<Author>AmericaJunkies
<Content>Worst Hotel We arrived from the UK and as soon as i saw this hotel i cried. We checked in and went straight to our hotel room my god it was shocking. The whole room was very bad and depressing and the bedding was so dirty that i could not even stay in the room and so spent the next few hours driving looking for another hotel and this was about 11pm at night. We eventualy went back to the hotel and asked to be moved (the penthouse suite) $200.00 extra. The room was large and beautiful sea views. The wardrobe doors were hanging off, the balcony door would not shut and the room was never cleaned. The only thing that was done was that the bed was made. I went to the toilet downstairs and it smelt very bad and when i looked around the toilet seat there was ***** on the lid and around the tiles.We are just average people that just wanted somewhere to sleep and this has to be a hotel from hell. I did not think that in this day and age there could be so much filth and in a hotel too.PLEASE PLEASE DO NOT STAY IN THIS HOTEL YOU PAY SO MUCH FOR HOLIDAYS AND TO HAVE IT RUINED. 
