<Author>textfast
<Content>Good choice on budget travel We spent two nights in the Ocean Terrace Hotel early February 2004 at a price of only 49 dollars a night for 2 people. We expected few, but got a lot. Nice, spacy and clean rooms with kitchen and freezer. Friendly staff, beautiful beach just across the (quiet) street. Many (Spanish) restaurants nearby. Far from the noice of South Beach and Art Deco District, to be reached by bus easily. We can surely recommend this hotel to anyone who travels budget. 
